{"tid":581004,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴4連敗   雲加：不用擔心","createTime":"2018-03-05T03:07:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T09:06:06.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e3afcb8087387a655a678e462f34f41c88cfae1c","tid":581004,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/05/110652_24dc0e1e1eae4b96831ba8d361bc12bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F05%2F110652_24dc0e1e1eae4b96831ba8d361bc12bc.png&h=0cf95944&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿仙奴上季未能取得歐聯資格，但總算捧到英足總盃攞番個尾彩，但兵工廠今季於足總盃第三圈已出局，在英聯賽盃決賽及英超連續兩場吞曼城3蛋，於歐霸盃16強又抽中AC米蘭，主帥雲加坦言：「我不會否認，今季比上季更差，因為我們上季奪得足總盃，在英超亦有75分。我們會在季尾分析一切，不用擔心，我一向都接受現實。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/體育/雲加承認今季仲衰過上季-117735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%2F%E9%9B%B2%E5%8A%A0%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E4%BB%8A%E5%AD%A3%E4%BB%B2%E8%A1%B0%E9%81%8E%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%A3-117735&d=KOyLHZc6IGti%2B7ug2mKjnV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=b6bb47ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/體育/雲加承認今季仲衰過上季-117735</a>"},{"pid":"a4abb499362215c1ae08a1c2e8fde00f21fa3be6","tid":581004,"uid":27324,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"接受現實仲棟係度?"},{"pid":"e623a1de1759ebc89308d681122e5b9deb7c1e3e","tid":581004,"uid":5652,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4abb499362215c1ae08a1c2e8fde00f21fa3be6","tid":581004,"uid":27324,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T03:53:14.000Z","msg":"接受現實仲棟係度?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:00:15.000Z","msg":"現實佢係仲棟係度！<br />\n係你地接受唔到姐"},{"pid":"7999a6e0ad2dc8eb39d285fdc0bc480c92a70de1","tid":581004,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"依家阿狗有45分<br />\n只要剩底幾場全勝 就會有<br />\n<br />\n<